data.description: ***LISTED UNDER APPRAISED VALUE***BACK ON MARKET DUE TO BUYERS FINANCING***Their loss is your gain! Summers will be a dream with this large in-ground pool & oversized freshly painted deck ready to host cookouts. The wooden privacy fence and plenty of lawn space make it great for friends & family to enjoy. The second floor of the home was updated with LVP flooring and freshly painted in June 2023. New roof 2019, New HVAC (upstairs) 2019 and pool pump is less than 2 years old. All major items have been taken care of now it's ready for your TLC and updates in the bathrooms and kitchen! Sellers are motivated! Bring all offers! Photos are virtually staged.Exterior of home, driveway & pool deck pressure washed (May 2023). New Pool Pump (2021). One Year Maintenance Membership provided by the seller with PunchList USA.
